{"tid":1052036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女兒天生無子宮冀生兒育女　55歲母自願地獄減肥38公斤代孕誕孫","createTime":"2019-03-08T04:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T15:04:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd259143a3f3fe9d7da2ceada718cbb76cf4eae","tid":1052036,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"母愛偉大！英國一名55歲母親，為了讓天生無子宮的女兒能有自己的愛情結晶，自願辭職並減重38公斤做代母，幫女兒誕下孩子。<br />\n據《BBC》報道，16歲時Tracey Smith已確診患上MRKH氏症候群」（Mayer-Rokitansky-K&uuml;ster-Hauser syndrome），即天生沒有子宮，無法生育。當知道自己無法生育時，她極為沮喪，第一個想法是：「誰會要我？誰會愛我？」因此她對愛情十分抗拒，直至她遇上現時的老公Adam Smith。<br />\nAdam指，起初Tracey十分抗拒戀愛，因為覺得自己「無法給予你想要的東西」，但他向Tracey說：<br />\n&quot;我的存在並非為了讓你給予我什麼，我是因你而存在。&quot;<br />\nAdam的一番話令Tracey大為感動，最後二人結婚，並漸漸希望利用現今科技，看看能否得到愛情結晶品。後來想到可以用人工受孕方式，再尋代母生子。<br />\n當55歲的Tracey媽媽Emma Miles知道女兒想要自己的孩子時，即馬上表示願意替她代孕。為了代孕她更辭去工作，努力減肥，成功減掉38公斤。<br />\nEmma表示，<br />\n&quot;做這決定一點也不難，任何人都會為自己孩子付出一切。&quot;<br />\n最終Emma於今年1月16日順利誕下重7磅2盎司的孫女。孩子順利誕下時，Tracey非常感動，直言「這或許是我一生中最美好的一日」。而女嬰亦命名為Emma Miles，以向婆婆致意。婆婆亦明言：<br />\n&quot;無論如何，她都是我的孫女，永遠都是Tracey的女兒，不是我的，我只是把她生出來而已。&quot;<br />\n不過基於當地代孕法規定，女嬰的出生證明母親欄只能填寫婆婆的名字，而母親Tracey及父親Adam只能申請「領養」女嬰。他們希望有朝一日可修改法例，解決代孕的法律爭議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2287431/baby_thumb_20190307_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2287431%2Fbaby_thumb_20190307_S_1024.jpg&h=d2b1771f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2287431/_105630232_mediaitem105630231_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2287431%2F_105630232_mediaitem105630231_1024.jpg&h=fff64110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2287431/_105630230_mediaitem105630229_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2287431%2F_105630230_mediaitem105630229_1024.jpg&h=003f7e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2287431/4_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2287431%2F4_1024.jpg&h=687d7057&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"115fdca096d96bec261264bc9eaa15eb966f43f2","tid":1052036,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"生出黎又冇字宮,孫女再搵呀嘛黎生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9731b24c2651715e63a43abb4f14b642c430021a","tid":1052036,"uid":194370,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"Adam Smith <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3d8ced3f01a371f0651e45cb39d290f9ade6c5","tid":1052036,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"115fdca096d96bec261264bc9eaa15eb966f43f2","tid":1052036,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"生出黎又冇字宮,孫女再搵呀嘛黎生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26752c7017754752bd4bc0b75e22583f4102bc08","tid":1052036,"uid":36911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"55歲個樣好似65歲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7a9d7016ba2157fb431ddbd15fd6c866f24e31","tid":1052036,"uid":85456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;我的存在並非為了讓你給予我什麼，我是因你而存在。&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呃蝦條個個男人都識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb95aace2a81325c5b880e7a1f872cbdd8c93a2","tid":1052036,"uid":1